1495
02:11:07,470 --> 02:11:08,960
抓紧点
Hold on tight, honey.

1496
02:12:05,500 --> 02:12:07,230
他在你后面！
He's behind you!

1497
02:12:08,030 --> 02:12:11,330
快降落，否则就杀了她！
Take this plane down, now! I'll kill her!

1498
02:12:11,900 --> 02:12:14,170
快降落，就现在！
Take it down, now!

1499
02:12:31,020 --> 02:12:32,990
天啊，想点办法呀！
My God, do something!

1500
02:12:39,060 --> 02:12:39,960
（发射钮）

1501
02:12:40,870 --> 02:12:41,830
你被炒了
You're fired.

1502
02:13:28,350 --> 02:13:29,410
好啦，没事了
It's okay.

1503
02:13:31,420 --> 02:13:32,380
达娜

1504
02:13:33,090 --> 02:13:35,280
甜心，都结束了
Honey, it's over.

1505
02:13:44,730 --> 02:13:46,060
嗨，小鬼头
Hi, pumpkin.

1506
02:13:49,040 --> 02:13:51,600
飞机刚一降落…
Just seconds after the jet landed...

1507
02:13:51,770 --> 02:13:53,700
身份不明的驾驶员…
the unidentified pilot was escorted...

1508
02:13:53,790 --> 02:13:55,400
马上由FBI护送离去
from the scene by Federal agents.

1509
02:13:55,640 --> 02:13:56,900
虽然我们不清楚…
Though it is unclear at this moment...

1510
02:13:57,040 --> 02:13:58,700
今早是哪个单位的探员
which agency was responsible...

1511
02:13:58,880 --> 02:14:01,310
这么戏剧化的结束了…
for the operation which ended the terrorist threat...

1512
02:14:01,480 --> 02:14:03,480
一场恐怖组织的威胁
so dramatically early this morning...

1513
02:14:03,580 --> 02:14:05,710
但据迈阿密警方的消息…
we've learned from Miami Police Do it properly.

1514
02:14:09,890 --> 02:14:14,600
（一年后）

1515
02:14:15,930 --> 02:14:20,130
一、二、三、四，开始拇指战
One, two, three, four, I declare a thumb war.

1516
02:14:20,270 --> 02:14:23,330
五、六、七、八，竖起拇指来
Five, six, seven, eight, try to keep your thumbs straight.

1517
02:14:23,500 --> 02:14:25,300
不要这样！停止
Don't! Stop it!

1518
02:14:25,500 --> 02:14:26,270
等一下
Wait!

1519
02:14:27,140 --> 02:14:28,330
我逮到你了
I got you!

1520
02:14:28,610 --> 02:14:31,240
你要听清楚规则
Just listen. Listen to the rules.

1521
02:14:36,320 --> 02:14:37,080
喂
Hello?

1522
02:14:37,250 --> 02:14:38,480
是波里斯和桃乐丝吗？
Boris and Doris?

1523
02:14:39,820 --> 02:14:40,790
我们有任务了
We're on.

1524
02:14:43,260 --> 02:14:44,810
是的，请说
Yes? Go ahead.

1525
02:15:13,020 --> 02:15:14,880
上校，真高兴又见到你
Colonel, how nice to see you again.

1526
02:15:15,050 --> 02:15:16,020
晚上好
Good evening.

1527
02:15:17,460 --> 02:15:18,420
她是谁？
Who was that?

1528
02:15:28,400 --> 02:15:30,960
情况如何？看到接头人了吗？
What's the scoop, team? You see your contact yet?

1529
02:15:31,340 --> 02:15:32,900
还没看到
Haven't seen him yet.

1530
02:15:34,610 --> 02:15:36,870
但是有个人，我倒想打个招呼
But I see somebody I'd like to say hello to.

1531
02:15:37,480 --> 02:15:39,210
再替你添点香槟
Let me pour you some more champagne.

1532
02:15:39,710 --> 02:15:41,510
我一定要扮得像个服务生
I got to keep up the waiter bit.

1533
02:15:42,050 --> 02:15:43,980
一般来说，监视有时很危险
These stakeouts can be tricky.

1534
02:15:44,750 --> 02:15:48,150
随时都会有生死攸关的情况发生
You never know when things might explode into a life-or-death situation.

1535
02:15:48,320 --> 02:15:50,350
如果真的发生你先躲起来
If it gets rough, stay low until it's over...

1536
02:15:50,490 --> 02:15:51,850
以后会联络你
and I'll contact you later.

1537
02:15:51,860 --> 02:15:53,190
最好把你的…
Maybe you should give me your...

1538
02:15:53,360 --> 02:15:55,490
嗨，卡洛斯，又见面了
So, we meet again, Carlos.

1539
02:15:59,770 --> 02:16:01,460
甜心，我就在这里解决他吧？
Honey, I'm just gonna do him right here, okay?

1540
02:16:02,470 --> 02:16:03,530
好呀
Go for it.

1541
02:16:05,500 --> 02:16:06,530
喔，天呀
Oh, God.

1542
02:16:13,050 --> 02:16:14,880
你不是没有害怕的权利吗？
Fear is not an option.

1543
02:16:27,560 --> 02:16:28,530
跳舞吧
Dance?

1544
02:16:31,830 --> 02:16:32,530
哦，不要啊

1545
02:16:32,700 --> 02:16:34,500
探戈
- Tango. - Here we go.

1546
02:16:50,820 --> 02:16:53,280
哈瑞、海伦，伙计们，拜托别跳了
Harry? Helen? Guys? Come on, now.

1547
02:16:53,520 --> 02:16:55,450
否则会分散注意力的
Let's not get distracted.

1548
02:16:55,650 --> 02:16:56,880
我们还有重要的事要办
We got some work to do.

1549
02:17:03,760 --> 02:17:05,290
好啦，别这样嘛
All right, guys. Come on.

1550
02:17:06,500 --> 02:17:08,100
你们最好正经点
You guys better get serious in there.

1551
02:17:08,260 --> 02:17:09,930
换成我就会很认真
I'd be serious if I was in there.

1552
02:17:12,440 --> 02:17:15,240
哈瑞，别不理我，那样很不礼貌
Don't ignore me, Harry. That's rude.

1553
02:17:18,540 --> 02:17:19,940
好啦，伙计们，别酱子
All right, guys. Come on.

1554
02:17:23,420 --> 02:17:24,780
这牵涉到国家安全
National security, guys.

1555
02:17:24,920 --> 02:17:26,680
是生死攸关的大事
Come on. Life and death.

1556
